## Parent Epic: Automatic Toolchain Synchronization (remote_compilation_helper-ayn)

## Task Description

Extend the RCH protocol to include toolchain information in selection requests and execution requests. The worker needs to know which toolchain to use for compilation.

## Changes Required

### 1. Update SelectionRequest
